entry.string: The caching configuration file is not writable by the web server. #(1) must be writable by the web server for the output caching to be managed by xarCacheManager.
entry.translation: Zee cecheeng cunffeegooreshun feele-a is nut vreeteble-a by zee veb serfer. #(1) moost be-a vreeteble-a by zee veb serfer fur zee ooootpoot cecheeng tu be-a muneged by xerCecheMuneger. Hurty flurty schnipp schnipp!
